findings.title: Unoptimized `withdrawalQueue` updating
findings.description: The current approach of iterating over the array to exclude duplicates or find item idx to remove and then calling `_organizeWithdrawalQueue` to normalize the array can lead to operations complexity reaching up to O(n^2).

findings.title: Code commentary doesn't comply with real implementation
findings.description: The rate limit has 'tokens per block' dimension in the code commentary but is assumed as a variable with 'tokens per second' dimension in the rate limit checker code.
